new.name: CVE-2025-1974
new.description: A minimal test tool to help detect annotation injection vulnerabilities in Kubernetes NGINX Ingress controllers. This script sends a crafted AdmissionReview request to simulate a potential exploit path from CVE-2025-1974 and checks for signs of misinterpreted annotations in controller logs.
